    <item>
      <title>嘉信理财的琼斯担心信贷市场因自满情绪而定价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/schwab-s-jones-worries-credit-markets-are-priced-for-complacency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国高等级公司债券利差徘徊在 25 年来最窄水平附近，明年可能进一步走低。嘉信理财公司的 Kathy Jones 认为这值得担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/schwab-s-jones-worries-credit-markets-are-priced-for-complacency</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 20:22:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Covalis Capital 出价 50 亿英镑收购泰晤士水务公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/covalis-capital-puts-up-5-billion-takeover-bid-for-thames-water</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，基础设施投资者 Covalis Capital 已提交一份 50 亿英镑（64 亿美元）的报价，以收购陷入困境的英国水务公司泰晤士水务公司，因为这家陷入困境的公用事业公司正在竞相筹集新资金，以免现金耗尽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/covalis-capital-puts-up-5-billion-takeover-bid-for-thames-water</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 20:16:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EQT 与 FT Partners 合作出售支付公司 Banking Circle</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/eqt-said-to-tap-ft-partners-to-sell-payments-firm-banking-circle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，EQT AB 正在与精品投资银行 Financial Technology Partners 合作，为支付服务提供商 Banking Circle 寻找买家，收购价格可能达到 30 亿至 40 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/eqt-said-to-tap-ft-partners-to-sell-payments-firm-banking-circle</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 20:06:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
